<h2>List of Poems</h2>

<ul>
  <% @poems.each do |poem| %>
    <li><%= link_to "\"#{poem.title}\", by #{poem.author}", poem %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>But please don't pick from this list.&nbsp;
It's <i>much</i> more fun if you have no clue what the poem is.&nbsp;
So, <%= link_to "ask for a random poem", random_poems_path %>.</p>
